directory: crates/ctx-verify/tests
summary: Integration-level behavioral tests for ctx-verify, covering parsers and orchestration via a canned FakeRunner. No real processes are spawned; all tool output is injected strings, making the suite hermetic and fast.
children:
  - checks.rs: Exercises the full check/parse/report pipeline against injected tool output without spawning real processes.
key_invariants:
  - FakeRunner returns ToolMissing for any key absent from its by_first_arg map, ensuring missing-tool paths are always exercised.
  - No real subprocesses are spawned in any test.